  "instructions": [
    "Brown ground beef in a large pot or slow cooker on high (don't stir initially to get a good sear)",
    "Dice onion and add to beef",
    "Mince garlic and add to pot",
    "Stir in tomato paste and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add spice blend (cumin, oregano, chili powder, garlic powder, onion powder) and toast in the fat for 1 minute",
    "Add diced tomatoes with green chilis, kidney beans, and chicken stock",
    "Add bay leaves and fish sauce if using",
    "Simmer for 30+ minutes, stirring occasionally",
